<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5829098>
    dc:description "Fig. 57. Stigmatomyces spp. A–F. S. crassicollis Thaxt. A–D. Mature thalli, from Leptocera fontinalis (A–B), from Spelobia luteilabris (C), and from Spelobia rufilabris (D). E–F. Primary appendages in detail. – G–K. S. divergatus Thaxt. G–I. Mature thalli. J. Primary appendage in detail. K. Perithecial tip in detail. Scale bars: 50 µm. Photographs from slides ZMUC C-F-124097 (A, E), ZMUC C-F-124017 (B, F), ZMUC C-F-124018 (C), ZMUC C-F-124019 (D), ZMUC C-F-123720 (G–H, J–K), ZMUC C-F- 123717 (I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5829098/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

